caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 In the diagram we also adopt a convention where indices for the larger
 dimensions 
\begin_inset Formula $D^{\prime}$
\end_inset

 as incoming arrows, and indices for the smaller dimension, 
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

 as outgoing arrows.
